description.title: Airbnb Clone
description.description: Airbnb Clone is a web application that allows you to search for places to stay in different cities. It has a login system, a search engine, and a map that shows the places available in the city you are looking for. It also has a calendar to select the dates of your stay and a carousel with the images of the place.
